px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Citron made his first pivot.&nbs=
p;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margi=
n: 0 0 1em 0;">During a conversation about Aurora&#8217;s future, the young=
