very earnest, rather drunk storyteller is not quite sure you heard them the=
 first time and will go bigger on their second attempt.&nbsp;</p><p style=
=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"=
>This time on better terms, Citron partnered up with Relan and set about cr=
